title: Husky Liners Husky Shield Paint Protection & Headlite Guards Product Video
description:
Husky Shield® is an innovative urethane paint and headlight protection film that is easy to install and does not ruin your vehicle's styling...like a bug shield. Invisible, pre-cut custom fit clear urethane film protects painted surfaces and headlights from rocks, bug
and scratches. Our unique adhesive and installation solution make installs almost error proof. Made in the USA
